        public StevensonReading​(double airTemperature,
                        double dewPoint,
                        double windSpeed,
                        int totalRain)
                 throws java.lang.IllegalArgumentException
        Constructs a weather reading in terms of the air temperature, dew point, wind speed, and the total rain.
        Parameters:
        airTemperature - the temperature of the air in Celsius
        dewPoint - the dew point in Celsius
        windSpeed - the speed of wind in miles per hour
        totalRain - the total rain received in the last 24 hours in mm
        Throws:
        java.lang.IllegalArgumentException - if any argument is negative or is not mathematically possible
